  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dd3 18\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A bus overturned and 18 were taken to the hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "18 passengers have been injured when a private bus running from Nuwara Eliya Udupusellawa to Batticaloa overturned at Mahawwa bend in Walapane, said Chief Inspector of Police N.D. Hettiarachchi, Station Commander of Walapane Police.",
        "The Chief Inspector of Police said that the bus carrying a group of people who had come from Batticaloa to attend a wedding ceremony in Udupussalla was returning to Batticaloa on (30) when the bus overturned on the main road in the area with a high wall.",
        "Five women who were injured in the accident have been admitted to the Rikilagaskada District General Hospital and the other injured have been admitted to the Walapane Regional Hospital.",
        "Walapane police, who are investigating the accident, said that the road the bus was traveling on was a road with a high embankment and a sudden technical fault in the bus's braking system caused the accident."
      ],
